## Installation & Usage

This project uses [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) for environment and
dependency management.

### Add to a uv project

```sh
uv add {{{projectName}}}
# or, to include the optional `[cli]` extra (installs the `graphsense` CLI):
uv add '{{{projectName}}}[cli]'
```

### Install from git

```sh
uv add 'git+https://{{gitHost}}/{{{gitUserId}}}/{{{gitRepoId}}}.git'
```

### One-off script usage

```sh
uv run --with {{{projectName}}} python my_script.py
```

Then import the package:

```python
import {{{packageName}}}
```

### Tests

Execute `uv run pytest` to run the tests.

